{"tid":1721017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"二噁英既毒理病徵同紫質症相近,會引起認知混亂及水皰","createTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T14:09:00.000Z","uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"05debf5c3533cb25fd3cf30950b90026c61ccb34","tid":1721017,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BA%8C%E5%99%81%E8%8B%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BA%258C%25E5%2599%2581%25E8%258B%25B1&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc67hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=96d992ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BA%8C%E5%99%81%E8%8B%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n戴奧辛是一種細胞毒。以TCDD為例，其進入人體後將誘導&delta;-胺基乙醯丙酸合酶（Aminolevulinic acid synthetase,ALAS）的產生，此酶為血紅素合成的限速酶。過多的ALAS會破壞細胞組織，<span style=\"color: red;\">並可能表現出類似卟啉症的病徵</span>[6]。戴奧辛可以誘導淋巴細胞凋亡，抑制殺傷性T細胞（cytotoxic T cell,Tc或CTL）的產生並促進免疫抑制因子的高度表達[7]，引起免疫系統調節功能障礙。戴奧辛亦能侵入DNA分子，誘發突變，由此而具有致畸與致癌作用。戴奧辛在體內不易代謝，可隨排泄物進入環境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%97%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25B4%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2597%2587&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc67hFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=b34ea64f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B4%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%97%87</a><br />\n紫質症<br />\n發作時的症狀有腹痛、胸痛、嘔吐、<span style=\"color: red;\">認知混亂</span>、便祕、發燒、高血壓及心跳過速等[1][2][3]，症狀通常會持續數天至數周[2]。可能的併發症有癱瘓、低血鈉症和癲癇發作[3]；乙醇、吸菸、內分泌的變化、斷食、壓力或服用特定的藥物都可能引起疾病的發作[2][3]。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果疾病進犯皮膚，陽光直曬可能會引起水皰或搔癢</span>[2]。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戴奧辛在體內不易代謝</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c95afcadf1a6c3ea402016353be0d992f019ae9","tid":1721017,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T14:09:00.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}